Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得找到基拉·汀斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么跟血腥約翰是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么馬上就要成為他下一個目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰干的  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  她說什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說血腥約翰左肩膀有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(193.8,204.8)}加利福尼亞  馬里布  簡的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-簡  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這么做  別扔下我這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  求你了  你身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣做是在自尋死路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(189,132)}兩天前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,132)\fad(0,400)}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紋身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以用那個來確定血腥約翰的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們只要一個個檢查疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪個人身上就紋身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰還不知道我發現紋身的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我們去查他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能血腥約翰會發現此事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在我們還沒機會接近他的時候就銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們打算怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再檢查是否有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接叫他們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他們會同意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒打算給他們選擇的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成行了  還有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊特·斯特爾斯因兩起謀殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被聯調局通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  二十多年前的懸案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都過去那么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局現在才跟進嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們肯定是有了什么新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法醫證據  目擊證人  -那斯特爾斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵就是這個  沒人知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連聯調局也不知道  斯特爾斯幾周前就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  但我們會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我配合你的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你揭露血腥約翰身份的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我說了好的  -說是說了  但你說的肯定不算數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事沒有商量的余地  簡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我百分百同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為我之前說得夠清楚了  探員們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道布萊特·斯特爾斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們也表達得很清楚了  你這說法我們不買賬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯把天眼組織的領導權留給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他卻沒有告訴你他躲藏在哪里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本說不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯自始至終
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都將教徒的需要放在他自己之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想讓我知道是因為他想保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因為他不想被人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不覺得布萊特·斯特爾斯擔心是否會被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來很有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯在我們這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界里的時間  是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我們說話的這會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在做好心理和身體上的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以擺脫我們這個物質世界的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是非常天真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常無知的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊特·斯特爾斯不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要將自己提升到一個新的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這種道行不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常艱難才能觸碰到這種高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然我們中有人對此是無法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡  加了一份奶油  一份糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  拉塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要準備好了的話鑒證小組就要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我查明他的身份  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我怕高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  有人來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰的案子有了重大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了一些新線索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  現在還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能信任誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道能不能信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰有一些位高權重的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但不能在這說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四  為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要時間找一個安全的見面地點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  在哪見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到了那天再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經犯過很多次錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是低估了血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再犯這種錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想知道線索  就要聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是麥卡利斯特警長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警長嗎  我是派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克  最近怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我打電話是有事想問你  -問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上個月我去納帕谷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說聽任我的調遣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說話算數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我是講信用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能指望你幫我個忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到那天我再告訴你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關于血腥約翰的事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們準備好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  伊夫林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  這是給您的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}派翠克·簡正在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你們在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將見證我升天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這個世界  飛升到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個世外的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要為我哀悼  我的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這并非逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  唐  你養的不是一個情婦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一個想要報復你  會毀掉你的瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作就是解決問題  你現在要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要給她開張支票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給她很大一筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后祈禱這事就這么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還沒完  也別擔心  唐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多種辦法可以讓一個女人閉嘴  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興見到你  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  請給我來一杯黑咖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上八點把我叫來干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個調查需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  如果你找我幫忙那這就很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  特蕾莎  我還不了解你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和簡對血腥約翰的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有進展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也許"  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要搞得這么神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的  為什么要瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們該不會覺得我是血腥約翰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是這么想的  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想找我問話  那就逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則就別把我扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果問不管用  我不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不為加調局工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在無法得到執法人員所能得到的保護了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么  你威脅我  -不是我  是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明天晚上想見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就會認為你是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他會找你麻煩的  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解簡的  你知道他身上發生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道血腥約翰對他做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我  我不會拿這個試探他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怕派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去和他見一面又有什么關系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和簡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再懷疑我是血腥約翰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后絕對不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了我算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特爾斯  -他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在哪兒  -我幫不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都為天眼組織工作這么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想抓他  我只想跟他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幫我這個忙  算我欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早你會需要我幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷·哈弗內說斯特爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架私人飛機供其往來國內不被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機主是一個名叫萊恩·帕克斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克斯  知道了  我去查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡到局里了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(189.6,266.4)}加州  帕羅奧多  帕羅奧多機場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉莫特先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  有什么可效勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周探員  瑞斯比探員  加調局的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想請你回答幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚有一架G6私人飛機降落在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注冊尾號為M550MT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約十一點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道飛機上的人是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  私人飛機不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供乘客名單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有碰巧見到有誰從飛機上下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  有汽車服務公司的人來接他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可能幫得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會正好知道那個汽車服務公司的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽車服務公司那邊怎么說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說昨晚從機場接到了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操著英國口音的銀發男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特爾斯  -我們也是這么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是厄瓜多爾領事館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舊金山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好樣的  你們倆去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  范佩爾  不如你一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們能利用這個優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒有  -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我沒問題的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-職責所在  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就干點跑腿的活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了  有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈弗內答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  斯特爾斯那邊怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾好像瞄準他的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就還剩一個血腥約翰案疑犯要約談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  伯特侖  我正往他辦公室走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-咱們那邊見嗎  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(190.8,267.2)}加利福尼亞  舊金山  厄瓜多爾領事館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯·范佩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次見到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次有何貴干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要你幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差你來  他可真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我到底能為派翠克·簡做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想見見你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上八點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我們上次一別  你變樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟我說你嫁給那個只會傻笑的呆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你會去見簡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能見他我再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很樂意  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸的是  鑒于我現在的境況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太能成行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說因為聯邦調查局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你功課做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不知道我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他們也就不知道你在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要是不肯見簡  他們就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的確變了  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去過厄瓜多爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很多很多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那傳教來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的人很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有個年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很窮  但野心勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他身上看到了些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我決定試著幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫他付學費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實也沒什么  但你猜怎么著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么多年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子已經是國務部長了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很為他高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邀請我住在這豪華的領事館里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這一片小小的外國領土上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外國領土  如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不受你們加調局  聯調局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與任何美國法律管轄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  格蕾斯  你的威脅不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  很高興能再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我跟簡問個好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去的時候隨手關門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啊  我感覺輕松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  案子有突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么案子  -血腥約翰案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上就能確定兇手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的確定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你們有了切實答案要立刻告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此案結束的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛和派翠克·簡談了點有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖那邊怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上鉤了  斯特爾斯那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不太好  -你找到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還有什么問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在厄瓜多爾領事館里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他在里面  我們就動不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來對付斯特爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會也不必跟你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我的說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霰彈槍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力夠大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于明天晚上的事  我們得談談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在場是因為你覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會阻止你殺血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是你不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像血腥約翰這種禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本連上庭受審的資格都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種人就該就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  讓我搞搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在執法部門干了快二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然就這么改變原則了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在血腥約翰案上嗎  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很驚訝  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我認識的最誠實的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情上  你絕不會騙我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明晚見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  我親愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近來還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  那么說你不是來找我聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚八點你要來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-派翠克  -不  你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你明晚八點來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則等到我再回來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這是領事館也保不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.17,0:24:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的話句句當真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.73,0:24:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將死之人還怕什么死亡威脅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝模作樣騙騙你那些信徒還行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.49,0:24:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不是裝的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還剩多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經擴散到血液了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無藥可醫了  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.24,0:24:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許兩周  也許一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:24:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.29,0:25:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是針對你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.37,0:25:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間對我來說太寶貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我還是需要你來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事如此重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.55,0:25:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終于接近他了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未有的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.84,0:25:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.87,0:25:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情況比你想象的復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.73,0:25:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在這兒還有別的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.79,0:25:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  事實正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.63,0:25:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們跟我到這里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.35,0:25:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等著我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.07,0:25:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我想呆在這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.06,0:25:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.30,0:25:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說聯調局是唯一的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  前門有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.78,0:26:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天眼組織的車
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在偷偷往外轉移什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.33,0:26:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時準備行動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.39,0:26:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即行動  行動  上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.13,0:26:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不許動  -不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在方向盤上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.26,0:26:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在我們能看見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.21,0:26:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好  先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能為你們效勞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯入局了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.19,0:27:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可有很長一段車程
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.43,0:27:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.80,0:27:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}晚上八點  馬里布  雪松街1309號見  走便道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.01,0:27:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}信息已發送
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么薩城警局只有等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.33,0:28:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想用職權壓人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.07,0:28:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有必要我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.53,0:28:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱文  回頭我再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.24,0:28:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.78,0:29:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看日落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本  有些話我想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早以前就應該跟你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.71,0:29:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.06,0:29:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚點再謝也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.22,0:29:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須現在就說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.75,0:29:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你對我意味著什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.28,0:30:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點忘了  我有個驚喜給你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.28,0:30:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這等我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.86,0:30:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.94,0:31:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.24,0:31:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(191.4,268)}加利福尼亞  馬里布  簡的住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.12,0:34:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.69,0:34:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.91,0:34:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州調查局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我要征用你的車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.72,0:34:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.78,0:34:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.62,0:35:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即下車  快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.74,0:35:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.39,0:35:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.10,0:35:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要報警
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.47,0:35:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.17,0:35:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-簡  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.23,0:35:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這么做  別扔下我這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.82,0:35:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.19,0:35:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  求你了  你身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.99,0:35:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.77,0:35:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣做是在自尋死路
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.86,0:35:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.26,0:37:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.65,0:37:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不早  來得正好  坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.72,0:37:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911  您遇到了什么緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.63,0:37:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州調查局的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.00,0:37:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎·里斯本探員
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.80,0:37:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請派警員到馬里布的雪松街1309號
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.84,0:37:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有探員需要立即支援
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓你們五個聚在一起是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.66,0:37:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.98,0:37:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人可能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們中的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.38,0:37:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  在我們幾個中間
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們其中之一是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.66,0:38:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是誰  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到這來就是為了找出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說這個房間里的某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我很確定  -太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.07,0:38:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證完全不荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.27,0:38:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證  我才不跟你在這兒胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.54,0:38:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步都別想往門口走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不準走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放輕松  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.36,0:38:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起來很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.68,0:38:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.49,0:38:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.08,0:38:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢把你們的槍拿出來  放在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.19,0:38:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.29,0:39:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.82,0:39:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.43,0:39:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.82,0:39:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.65,0:39:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這一刻  我等了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.91,0:39:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年來  血腥約翰一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.76,0:39:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們中的某個人一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.97,0:39:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很謹慎  除了這次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.68,0:39:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次  你露出馬腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.83,0:39:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我說了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.77,0:39:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告訴我殺她的人  也就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.21,0:39:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.82,0:39:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.88,0:39:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都得
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:39:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻動手
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始脫吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.97,0:40:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.33,0:40:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.95,0:40:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.00,0:40:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想得那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你弄錯了  -住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.82,0:40:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.94,0:40:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.51,0:40:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.65,0:41:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.32,0:41:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他們倆那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.21,0:41:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別動
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.34,0:41:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.51,0:41:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墻邊站著  快
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.31,0:41:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.69,0:41:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.62,0:42:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
